The .bin files 
Application: fault_injector.bin
Bootloader: bootloader.bin
Partition: partition-table.bin

use an "esptool" for flashing to your esp32 s3.
ESP32 S3 Web Flasher https://esptool.spacehuhn.com
This is all just in the begining phrase, do not attempt this unless you are an advance hardware tinker.
